# Pseudocode:
# - Define two variables to hold cookie values: City and Date (format yyyy-MM-dd).
# - For the CookieForecast request, add a Cookie header: "Cookie: city={{City}}; date={{Date}}".
# - Preserve existing requests; only augment the CookieForecast request with headers.
# - Users can change @City and @Date at the top; the request will pick them up dynamically.

@WebApiDemo_HostAddress = https://localhost:7074
@City = Taipei
@Date = 2025-09-23

GET {{WebApiDemo_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{WebApiDemo_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/CookieForecast
Accept: application/json
Cookie: city={{City}}; date={{Date}}

###
